{"tid":1514070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我認輸了，頭先位絲打叫口號咁大聲而我就無叫到","createTime":"2019-08-28T14:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:00:42.000Z","uid":243854,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdcacd27c731f723291e2047a19ae7d39110021","tid":1514070,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買完嘢返到樓下，聽到今次叫口號嘅人比以往多，真係幾開心<br />\n最令我估唔到身後有個港女FEEL嘅絲打一聽到光復香港，即刻衝去天橋邊大叫時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我只能夠柒下柒下咁行住睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(你要我屌警犬我可以好大聲，上台講嘢都唔怕，但唔知點解咁叫口號反而驚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nBTW我決定咗，聽日我會第一個叫口號先，希望一眾毒撚可以一齊咁做，畀返啲男子氣蓋大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：佐助型毒撚"},{"pid":"0775cb1507cfd66c2be94ff63e991a215b00b04f","tid":1514070,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"8df895e98d7a4ff1a17f08bf656e6d0487b12831","tid":1514070,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dbb283e34e03d0964bc3b915b3aa3e3d08a174","tid":1514070,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"3298b97d189a7d86619d8496e87e7692565c442a","tid":1514070,"uid":220695,"like":0,"dislike":0